# @bloomneo/uikit rules

## Import
- Always: `import { X } from '@bloomneo/uikit'`
- Never deep-import: `@bloomneo/uikit/button` is for tree-shaking only
- Types: `import { type DataTableColumn } from '@bloomneo/uikit'`

## Required setup (main.tsx)
- `import '@bloomneo/uikit/styles'` -- core CSS (no fonts)
- `import '@bloomneo/uikit/styles/fonts'` -- optional, only if theme uses built-in fonts
- Wrap app: `<ThemeProvider theme="base" mode="light"><ToastProvider /><ConfirmProvider><App /></ConfirmProvider></ThemeProvider>`
- FOUC prevention: drop `foucScript()` from `@bloomneo/uikit/fouc` into `index.html` `<head>`

## Component picking
- Form with labels/errors/a11y: use `<FormField>` wrapper, not raw `<Label>` + `<Input>`
- Password fields: use `<PasswordInput>`, not `<Input type="password">`
- Tables with sort/search/pagination: use `<DataTable>`, not raw `<Table>`
- Confirm before destructive action: use `useConfirm()` (promise-based), not manual `<Dialog>`
- Toast notifications: use `toast.success()`/`toast.error()`, not custom alerts
- Empty lists: use `<EmptyState>`, not ad-hoc placeholder divs
- Page titles with breadcrumbs/actions: use `<PageHeader>`

## Layouts (pick one per route)
- Dashboard/SaaS: `<AdminLayout>` with `.Header`, `.Sidebar`, `.Content`
- Marketing/landing: `<PageLayout>` with `.Header`, `.Content`, `.Footer`
- Login/signup: `<AuthLayout scheme="card">`
- Mobile (Capacitor): `<MobileLayout>`
- Browser extension: `<PopupLayout>`
- Custom/blank: `<BlankLayout>`

## Prop patterns
- Button variants: `default | destructive | outline | secondary | ghost | link`
- DataTable is generic: `<DataTable<User> data={users} columns={cols} />`
- DataTable columns: `{ id, header, accessorKey, sortable?, cell? }`
- FormField: `<FormField label="X" required helper="hint"><Input /></FormField>`
- Confirm: `const ok = await confirm({ title, description, tone: 'destructive' })`
- ThemeProvider themes: `base | elegant | metro | studio | vivid`

## Styling
- Use semantic Tailwind classes: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`
- Use `text-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-muted`, `bg-card`
- Use `cn()` from `@bloomneo/uikit` for conditional class merging

## Hooks & utilities
- `useTheme()` -- get/set theme and mode
- `useConfirm()` -- promise-based confirmation dialog
- `useMediaQuery()`, `useBreakpoint()`, `useActiveBreakpoint()` -- responsive
- `useApi()` -- data fetching
- `useLocalStorage()` -- persistent state
- `formatCurrency()`, `formatNumber()`, `formatDate()`, `timeAgo()`, `formatBytes()`

## Never do
- Never hardcode colors (`bg-white`, `text-black`) -- use semantic tokens
- Never deep-import in generated code (`@bloomneo/uikit/button`)
- Never skip `ThemeProvider` -- components break without it
- Never skip `ToastProvider` if using `toast()`
- Never skip `ConfirmProvider` if using `useConfirm()`
- Never use `<Dialog>` for simple yes/no confirms -- use `useConfirm()`
- Never use `@voilajsx/uikit` -- old scope, frozen at 1.4.0
- Never create separate CSS files for theming -- use the preset system
